  <Scope>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
  <LocalizationId>k__BackingField: HealthBarTutorialDescription
  <TextId>k__BackingField: 
  _editRussian: 0
  <Russian>k__BackingField: "\u042D\u0442\u043E \u0448\u043A\u0430\u043B\u0430 \u0432\u0430\u0448\u0435\u0433\u043E
    \u0437\u0434\u043E\u0440\u043E\u0432\u044C\u044F. \u0415\u0441\u043B\u0438 \u0448\u043A\u0430\u043B\u0430
    \u043E\u043F\u0443\u0441\u0442\u0438\u0442\u0441\u044F \u0434\u043E \u043D\u0443\u043B\u044F,
    \u0432\u044B \u043F\u0440\u043E\u0438\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0435\u0442\u0435."
  <RussianSprite>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
  _editEnglish: 0
  <English>k__BackingField: This is the school of your health. If the scale drops
    to zero, you lose.
  <EnglishSprite>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
  _editTurkish: 0
  <Turkish>k__BackingField: "Buras\u0131 sizin sa\u011Fl\u0131k okulunuz. \xD6l\xE7ek
    s\u0131f\u0131ra d\xFC\u015Ferse kaybedersiniz."
  <TurkishSprite>k__BackingField: {fileID: 0}
